                           <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-200-18471122 t18471122-200-punishment-170"></join>DEATH</rs>
                     </hi> recorded.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Serjeant.</hi>
